{"tid":10264,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"深度遊撚，你問我答。","createTime":"2016-11-29T01:02:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-13T08:13:37.000Z","uid":37565,"like":3,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"436b0ad7e94dbda2adf7e2bd9fd75f075c9fbe4e","tid":10264,"uid":37565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T01:02:16.000Z","msg":"從來沒走馬看花。<br />\n<br />\n大學三年，去過 Ho Chi Minh City, the Everest Base Camp, Tibet, Paris, London, Berlin, Budapest, Vienna &amp; Munich。 <br />\n<br />\n每個地方 stay 超過十日，最多係三十幾日。去之前仲會學下當地語言。<br />\n<br />\n問題從來都唔係有咩好玩，係你有冇時間、金錢去經歷同了解。<br />\n<br />\n第四年， plan 緊去南美/非州。<br />\n<br />\n歡迎討論。"},{"pid":"31135741d6a96ae1cd6dc9a908c3719f8e997852","tid":10264,"uid":26931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T01:03:14.000Z","msg":"窮遊? 定本身有錢?"},{"pid":"32b2eaab09a9ea0026a748d6de211f3a4d9f559b","tid":10264,"uid":37565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T01:04:15.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"f20995190eeaf76f85d8edc1435bec55e3ac1502","tid":10264,"uid":37565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T01:10:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>窮遊? 定本身有錢?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n學生喳。<br />\n<br />\n應洗得洗。自問唔 buy 一般人窮遊既 concepts 。去旅行唔應該係鬥窮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係應該用手頭上既金錢，睇/做自己想睇/做既野。<br />\n<br />\n其實洗費唔會好大。好似住一晚簡單 hotel 好似係中歐既 A&amp;O 都係 hkd100/200一晚啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1cb1e0c3b7466b0dd7df83b4b8946911d74bc62","tid":10264,"uid":32680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T01:15:09.000Z","msg":"上the Everest Base Camp是咪要練好體能先上到？"},{"pid":"842be39a27e9cc81783a2210ecbf5368289ca74d","tid":10264,"uid":37565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T01:23:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上the Everest Base Camp是咪要練好體能先上到？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />其實我係西藏個邊既 EBC 經拉薩，包司機，坐四驅車去。六個 friends有五個都唔 fit唔 sporty 冇特別不良反應。有一個曾經係港隊都冇特別不良反應。純粹好涷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係第一日到拉薩有小小唔舒服，有個女仔，跟住都冇野。"},{"pid":"6c7dda0217dc90ff9d8b3e3480ef3754a409f202","tid":10264,"uid":37565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T01:25:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有負皮？"},{"pid":"cdf35827642ccbf690c90a9de41a578bec8a0826","tid":10264,"uid":37565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T02:58:19.000Z","msg":"輕輕一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ff18d73d51853cc0a87e32a6118a22bac41e037","tid":10264,"uid":37565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T03:34:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/j2nkdig5\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fj2nkdig5&h=8f5eed3e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nBudapest"},{"pid":"178dfd724e2ae530a7fea897a0eb6b093840002c","tid":10264,"uid":37086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T06:22:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ba378190848a03c712eb7bb7c03a360f6da3eb40","tid":10264,"uid":37565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T06:43:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/bndxe1fg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fbndxe1fg&h=eb61b95c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nMunich 街拍"},{"pid":"7223cfd29a14da1f0a36379cfa7a2f70a1b13ab4","tid":10264,"uid":37086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T07:13:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"19266f09a646ed091c056faabe4c006f4c742aa8","tid":10264,"uid":37565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T07:19:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"http://na.cx/i/rn2HQUP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Frn2HQUP.jpg&h=8b3e6b63&s={SIZE}\" /><br 